-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

dijit.Editor
dijit.Menu
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Documentation

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Plugin Installation instructions

Get the dojox/editor folder (and dojox/editor/plugins) from the 
dojox SVN repository. Include the Editor and plugins in your page:

dojo.require("dijit.Editor");
dojo.require("dojox.editor.plugins.TablePlugins");

And the style sheet:

<link href="[path]dojox/editor/plugins/resources/editorPlugins.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" />

See dojox/editor/plugins/tests/editorTablePlugs.html for a markup example
